  "description": "<b>近日，谷歌工程部总管Ray Kurzweil做了一个大胆的预测：人类将很快就会开发出可以永生的先进技术。</b>据<i>CNBC</i>报道，Kurzweil在全球未来2045世界大会上 (Global Future 2045 World Congress)指出，在未来的10到20年时间里，人类的平均寿命将会大大提高，甚至无需15年时间，人类就会到达一个临界点--因科学技术进步延长的寿命长于正常时光消耗的寿命。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d6dc1f7/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241543.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241543.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241543.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241543.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%88%E5%BF%AB%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://